scene.message:
Yukino: !{wait_fr:15}{nl}
The courtyard{wait_fr:15}...{wait_fr:15}...{wait_fr:15}?{nl}
What's going on?!{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Saeko: Teacher?{wait_fr:30}{nl}
Ah, you mean Saeko.{waitkey}{clearbox}Poor Saeko.{nl}
Hffffff...{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Huh?{waitkey}"Saeko"{wait_fr:30} - that's you,{nl}
isn't it?{waitkey}{clearbox}Snap out of it!{nl}
Did you hit your head?{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Saeko: Hffffff...{nl}
"I'll be fine even if I{nl}
put on the mask"?{waitkey}{clearbox}Hffffff...{nl}
Ahahahaha.{waitkey}Saeko was always like that.{waitkey}{clearbox}Confident,{wait_fr:30} self-centered{wait_fr:30}...{nl}
If it meant being the center{nl}
of attention, she'd never{waitkey}think of others.{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Saeko: A joke?{waitkey}Take a good look around.{nl}
Hffffff... does this seem{nl}
like a joke to you?{waitkey}{clearbox}Beautiful, isn't it?{nl}
A pure landscape, all of it{nl}
wrapped in eternal silence.{waitkey}{clearbox}You too shall don eternal{nl}
ice and pass the ages,{nl}
beautiful forever.{waitkey}Now, come to me.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: "Come to me"...?{nl}
What're you saying at a{nl}
time like this?!{waitkey}Teacher or not...{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Saeko: Oh my,{nl}
what a cute young lady.{waitkey}{clearbox}Hffffff...{nl}
Come closer, dear. I'll{nl}
grant you eternal beauty too.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Yuka, stay back!!{waitkey}It's the mask{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}{nl}
The mask has taken her over!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Monster, what's your game?!{nl}
Pull anything on Ms. Saeko{nl}
and I won't stand for it!!{waitkey}{ret}

Mask: "Taken over"{wait_fr:30}, you say?{nl}
How unkind of you.{waitkey}{clearbox}And who was it that broke{nl}
the seal, I wonder?{wait_fr:30}{nl}
Who put the mask on freely?{waitkey}{clearbox}Besides... calling someone{nl}
a "monster" is rather rude,{nl}
don't you think, dear?{waitkey}{clearbox}Yes... after the mask,{wait_fr:30}{nl}
why not call me the{nl}
"Snow Queen"{wait_fr:30}?{waitkey}Hffffff...{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Don't mess with me!{nl}
What will you do with{nl}
Ms. Saeko?!{waitkey}{ret}

Snow Queen: I'll make her{nl}
a sacrifice, my spirited{nl}
young lady.{waitkey}{ret}

Snow Queen: Yes, a sacrifice.{waitkey}Sacrifice Saeko, so full{nl}
of hope,{waitkey}{clearbox}and the silence of despair{wait_fr:30}{nl}
- the "Eternal Night" -{nl}
will come.{waitkey}{ret}

Snow Queen: A spirited girl.{nl}
Very well, I'll give her back.{waitkey}{clearbox}But unless this mask comes{nl}
off, Saeko won't return,{nl}
and the school stays frozen.{waitkey}{clearbox}Walk around a bit and you'll{nl}
see - there's no leaving the{nl}
school. There's no escape.{waitkey}{clearbox}Accept the "Eternal Night,"{nl}
or remove Saeko's mask...{waitkey}One of the two.{waitkey}{ret}

Snow Queen: Hffffff...{waitkey}{clearbox}Struggle all you like.{nl}
Nothing is more beautiful{nl}
than despair after struggle.{waitkey}{clearbox}It seems I'll gather plenty{nl}
of beautiful despair.{nl}
How delightful.{waitkey}{ret}

Snow Queen's Voice:{nl}
Hffffff... Just try touching{nl}
her carelessly.{waitkey}{clearbox}Mask and Saeko alike{nl}
would shatter to{nl}
pieces.{waitkey}{clearbox}The rituals take time, so{nl}
there's a while yet before{nl}
the "Eternal Night" comes.{waitkey}Until then, let's play a game.{waitkey}{ret}

Snow Queen's Voice:{nl}
The school has become an ice{nl}
castle with three towers,{waitkey}each with its own guardian.{waitkey}{clearbox}If you can defeat them before{nl}
the clock in each tower{nl}
strikes twelve...{waitkey}{clearbox}then I shall return the{nl}
frozen Saeko and the school{nl}
to how they were.{waitkey}{clearbox}I must leave the mask, my{nl}
vessel, and prepare to{nl}
summon the "Eternal Night."{waitkey}{clearbox}Enjoy yourselves until then.{nl}
Hffffff...{nl}
Now, farewell.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: "Farewell"?{nl}
Hey, wait!!{nl}
{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}Don't leave us...{waitkey}{clearbox}No way...{nl}
Wh-{wait_fr:15}wh-{wait_fr:15}what do we do!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: This is all your{nl}
fault, {ctl0f:1}!!{waitkey}{clearbox}You're the one who found{nl}
that creepy mask - that's{nl}
why this happened!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Take responsibility!{waitkey}You're a man, aren't you!!{waitkey}Say something!!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Yuka! Stop it!!{waitkey}{clearbox}No use saying that now -{nl}
it won't change anything.{waitkey}{clearbox}{ctl0f:1} didn't do it on{nl}
purpose, knowing this{nl}
would happen.{waitkey}{ret}
